Title: Your Marksman License
Text:
Official Notification: Marksman License Approval.

Head to Gramados Town Hall to finish the paperwork.
CompleteText: The Marksman License is a symbol of precision, discipline, and responsibility. Only a select few earn it, and those who do are often called upon for high-level tasks, competitive events, and professional hunting contracts. With this license, your reputation in the shooting community will grow, and doors to new challenges will open.
